data.description: Imagine waking up and sipping your morning coffee on the back deck... well now you can in your beautifully maintained and thoughtfully updated home in Churchland school district. This 4 bedroom house has all the space you could need while also providing a wonderful entertaining area for any size gathering. The wooded yard gives privacy while still allowing for plenty of space for a deck, fire pit, shed and so much more! Bathrooms, kitchen and and some flooring have all been recently updated, newly painted exterior shutters and freshly pressure washed; this house is ready for you to call it home! BRAND NEW electrical panel, new encapsulated crawlspace and HVAC was just serviced! Seller is willing to pay for one year home warranty for new buyers. Don’t let this one get away!
